I needed a haircut to look like a person again. I Went  into this sports clips and was greeted with a genuine smile and hello. Not too many place do that anymore. I got the full treatment and wasn't disappointed one bit. Before I came in, I read reviews and everyone complains about how much it is. I don't see why... You pay for quality and the experience. If you want to be treated like a person and not another number, DEFINITELY come here! It's really nice finally finding a place that actually cares. Ohhh and they have this shampoo that makes your head feel tingly. Pick up some of that too. I will be back for more!

