I have been looking for a place that serves amazing wings with some style. This placed does that for me. From the koolaid fountain to the cutout metal chicken on the wall, this place is the shit. Their wings are definitely the best wings I have ever had in AZ. Other places are super greasy, and make me poop right after. But this place has defied the odds with my bowel issue and love of wings.  I will definitely be back and become a loyal customer. I recommend this place to everyone.

